{"tid":38000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[獅子山精神]怕返工遲到被炒 亞馬遜員工公司外露營過","createTime":"2016-12-13T15:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T05:58:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"430824f0a5cf568a0daf90f1df1e4543efd5e8b6","tid":38000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thecourier.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/12/Sbro_Amazon_Tents_For_Workers_Dunfermline-10.jpg-e1481295229652-620x372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecourier.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F12%2F2016%2F12%2FSbro_Amazon_Tents_For_Workers_Dunfermline-10.jpg-e1481295229652-620x372.jpg&h=3905d39f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n怕返工遲到被炒 亞馬遜員工公司外露營過夜 <br />\n<br />\n準時上班幾乎是每一位打工仔都要遵守的事，但有沒有試過為準時上班，就在公司外面過夜？電子商務巨頭亞馬遜（Amazon）在英國的分公司就有員工為了能準時上班，而在公司附近的樹林裡露營過夜。 <br />\n<br />\n英國每日郵報（Daily Mail）報導，有人看見至少3名亞馬遜員工在樹林裡搭帳篷，引來外界不少批評。有員工形容亞馬遜是「差勁的雇主」，並且批評法夫郡（Fife）物流中心的工作準則。 <br />\n<br />\n選擇露營的員工指，比起從位於伯斯（Perth）的家坐車來上班既慳時間又可以慳錢，但他的紮營設備在前日下午不翼而飛。 <br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜位於蘇格蘭法夫郡丹弗姆林（Dunfermline）的物流中心聘用了大約1,500名長期員工，另外又聘請了4,000個臨時職位來協助處理聖誕和新年期間的貨件。 <br />\n<br />\n報導又指亞馬遜員工每週工時高達60小時，卻只能賺取略高於最低工資的薪金，並且受到嚴苛的待遇，令公司一直備受評擊。 <br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜近日成為全球最有價值零售品牌，市值1,980億英鎊，員工時薪卻只有7.35英鎊（約港幣72元），僅略高於當地最低工資的標準，員工倘若未能爭分奪秒地追蹤線上消費者所訂購的商品，還有可能面臨處分。亞馬遜駁斥上述指控，指公司非常珍惜與員工「直接對話的文化」。 <br />\n<br />\n入面有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thecourier.co.uk/fp/news/local/fife/325800/exclusive-amazon-workers-sleeping-in-tents-near-dunfermline-site/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecourier.co.uk%2Ffp%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Ffife%2F325800%2Fexclusive-amazon-workers-sleeping-in-tents-near-dunfermline-site%2F&d=8z1brvdlsQg%2B6kaZjdJoAksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=05b82c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thecourier.co.uk/fp/news/local/fife/325800/exclusive-amazon-workers-sleeping-in-tents-near-dunfermline-site/</a>"},{"pid":"444fb1ba29b95d47ff69b279a4bdd992510267c7","tid":38000,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"屌，係公司訓覺不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baad6150b19a73321f29656da04e904d39c52648","tid":38000,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"港奴去到會點？"},{"pid":"18b7e38fdbf29a324981a652946a6c35e0c20d82","tid":38000,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，係公司訓覺不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個排等錢洗,想返多d時間 試過訓m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89260a66206e3e0e54c25293fe86c291cbae6f4b","tid":38000,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"fife=快富街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af65d844e9a1a40fd48b4f691b03939c76d39e83","tid":38000,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"72蚊<br />\n係香港一個double重唔知足<br />\n廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca5db722b48c0cbf2c4d2acace104ea9594a5a5","tid":38000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc8d19de7ccbcadc4ec837fa5b0dd4382dffb6a","tid":38000,"uid":51233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://www.thecourier.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/12/Sbro_Amazon_Tents_For_Workers_Dunfermline-10.jpg-e1481295229652-620x372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecourier.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F12%2F2016%2F12%2FSbro_Amazon_Tents_For_Worke